<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Runtime Architecture - Node.js Interview Playground</title>
    <%- include('../partials/styles') %>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <%- include('../partials/header') %>
        <%- include('../partials/nav') %>
        
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Node.js Runtime Architecture</h2>
            <p>Understanding V8 engine, libuv, and how Node.js works under the hood.</p>
            
            <h3>Runtime Information</h3>
            <div class="code-block">
                <pre><code>Node.js Version: <%= info.nodeVersion %>
V8 Version: <%= info.v8Version %>
Platform: <%= info.platform %>
Architecture: <%= info.arch %>
Process ID: <%= info.pid %>
Uptime: <%= Math.floor(info.uptime) %> seconds</code></pre>
            </div>
            
            <h3>Memory Usage</h3>
            <div class="code-block">
                <pre><code>Heap Used: <%= (info.memoryUsage.heapUsed / 1024 / 1024).toFixed(2) %> MB
Heap Total: <%= (info.memoryUsage.heapTotal / 1024 / 1024).toFixed(2) %> MB
RSS: <%= (info.memoryUsage.rss / 1024 / 1024).toFixed(2) %> MB</code></pre>
            </div>
            
            <h3>System Information</h3>
            <div class="code-block">
                <pre><code>CPU Cores: <%= info.systemInfo.cpus %>
Total Memory: <%= (info.systemInfo.totalMemory / 1024 / 1024 / 1024).toFixed(2) %> GB
Free Memory: <%= (info.systemInfo.freeMemory / 1024 / 1024 / 1024).toFixed(2) %> GB</code></pre>
            </div>
            
            <div class="key-points">
                <h3>Key Concepts:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>V8:</strong> JavaScript engine - compiles JS to machine code</li>
                    <li><strong>libuv:</strong> Event loop, thread pool, async I/O</li>
                    <li><strong>Single-threaded:</strong> Event loop runs on one thread</li>
                    <li><strong>Multi-threaded I/O:</strong> libuv thread pool handles I/O operations</li>
                    <li><strong>Non-blocking:</strong> I/O operations don't block event loop</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
